Release Notes for Version 3.11.0
================================

Overview
--------

Release 3.11.0 is the first release in Errata Tool 3.11. It closes [54
bugs and RFEs][buglist].

Major enhancements in this release include a new Product Security
Approval workflow step for RHSA, several API additions, revised and
integrated API documentation, and TPS and RPMDiff scheduling
improvements.

Additionally, during the 3.10.6 development period, [7 bug
fixes][hotfixes] were shipped in releases 3.10.6.1, 3.10.6.2, 3.10.6.3
and 3.10.6.4, mostly consisting of changes to support the release of
RHEL 7.1.

